column5: To all OFC'rs making the trek to the B of Q this weekend. Be safe, catch a lot of fish, take lotsa pictures, have a cool one for me.  John
Good luck and a safe drive.  I'll see you all Sat night!  Stan

Yep be safe all, looks like crappy driving weather out here in the east end today!  We'll see ya out there, maybe pop in for a brownie and a Diplip BBQ saturday night.  Maybe even catch Roy and DouG in mid stream Simon and Garfunkal again!  Good Luck.
Thanks John...we made it both ways and were last to leave TTBOMK..so all are home safe.
